Please save the date for our 2019 Graduate Showcase happening on 14 November at our campus in Salt River. You'll get to meet the talent behind the magic and explore the very best innovative ideas and extraordinary craftsmanship that the final year students from our BA in Visual Communications as well as our Certificate in Graphic Design, Certificate in User-centered Design and Certificate in Creating Digital Content programmes have to offer the industry. Come and join the fun for an evening of creative thinking and festivity! <img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1909/518730-625x442.jpg" alt="Save the date - 2019 Red &amp; Yellow Graduate Showcase" width="625" height="442">